org.apache.flink.runtime.util

类 EvictingBoundedList<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.util.EvictingBoundedList<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - type of the list elements
    所有已实现的接口:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class EvictingBoundedList<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<T>, java.io.Serializable
    This class implements a list (array based) that is physically bounded in maximum size, but can virtually grow beyond the bounded size. When the list grows beyond the size bound, elements are dropped from the head of the list (FIFO order). If dropped elements are accessed, a default element is returned instead.

    The list by itself is serializable, but a full list can only be serialized if the values are also serializable.

      • map

        public <R> EvictingBoundedList<R> map(EvictingBoundedList.Function<T,R> transform)
        Creates a new list that replaces its elements with transformed elements. The list retains the same size and position-to-element mapping.

        Note that null values are automatically mapped to null values.

        类型参数:
        R - The type of the elements in the result list.
        参数:
        transform - The function used to transform each element
        返回:
        The list with the mapped elements
